title: UNTIL DAWN (ENGLISH) (A)
overview: One year after her sister Melanie mysteriously disappeared, Clover and her friends head into the remote valley where she vanished in search of answers. Exploring an abandoned visitor center, they find themselves stalked by a masked killer and horrifically murdered one by one…only to wake up and find themselves back at the beginning of the same evening.

title: RAID 2 (HINDI WITH ENGLISH SUBTITLE) (UA 7+)
overview: A fiery Income Tax officer, Amay Patnaik, confronts the corrupt nexus in Bhoj. Beneath the veneer of honesty lies a sinister operation tied to Dada Bhai, a revered politician. As Amay unravels layers of deceit buried in fields and fortresses, one question looms: will justice prevail, or will power silence the truth?

title: RETRO (TAMIL) (UA 16+)
overview: In the 1990s, the son of a dreaded gangster attempts to leave his violent life for his true love.

title: KESARI CHAPTER 2
overview: Sir Chettur Sankaran Nair was known for being a passionate advocate for social reforms and a firm believer in the self-determination of India.

title: SINNERS
overview: Trying to leave their troubled lives behind, twin brothers return to their hometown to start again, only to discover that an even greater evil is waiting to welcome them back.

title: A MINECRAFT MOVIE
overview: Four misfits find themselves struggling with ordinary problems when they are suddenly pulled through a mysterious portal into the Overworld: a bizarre, cubic wonderland that thrives on imagination. To get back home, they'll have to master this world while embarking on a magical quest with an unexpected, expert crafter, Steve.

title: PADDINGTON IN PERU
overview: Paddington travels to Peru to visit his beloved Aunt Lucy, who now resides at the Home for Retired Bears. With the Brown Family in tow, a thrilling adventure ensues when a mystery plunges them into an unexpected journey through the Amazon rainforest and up to the mountain peaks of Peru.
tagline: A little bear goes a long way.

title: GROUND ZERO
overview: An Indian army officer embarks on a mission leading to India’s most successful counter-terrorism operation in history.

title: THE AMATEUR
overview: After his wife is tragically killed in a London terrorist attack, a CIA cryptographer demands his bosses go after the killers. When it becomes clear they won’t act due to conflicting internal priorities, he blackmails the agency into training him and letting him go after them himself.
